  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    NomParserConstants
    Token literal values and constants.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AttachedGroup
    Holds data on a specific functional group or substituent.
    MoleculeBuilder
    Takes in parsed Tokens from NomParser and contains rules to convert those tokens to a Molecule.
    NomParser Deprecated
    The OPSIN (http://opsin.ch.cam.ac.uk/) tool offers a more comprehensive alternative to this parsers functionality.
    NomParserTokenManager
    Token Manager.
    SimpleCharStream
    An implementation of interface CharStream, where the stream is assumed to contain only ASCII characters (without unicode processing).
    Token
    Describes the input token stream.
